  "instructions": [
    "Heat the ghee in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the chicken breast pieces and cook until they are browned.",
    "Add the Thai green curry paste and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the chopped nuka-pickle and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Pour in the coconut milk and stir well.",
    "Add the salt and black pepper and stir well.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook until the chicken is cooked through.",
    "Stir in the chopped cilantro and serve hot."
